data.description: 80 wooded acres with multiple ponds! You'll want to reconsider your homestead dream once you see this total package with a 2,300+ square foot home built in 2006. The house features multiple spacious living areas - an open kitchen with dining and center island, and a bright living room with cathedral knotty pine ceilings. Off the living room you'll find tranquility on the large deck overlooking the stocked pond, and a plethora of wildlife. The primary bedroom is the perfect sanctuary, with en suite bathroom, clawfoot bathtub for soaking, convenient laundry in closet, and a built-in gun safe. In addition to the two bedrooms, there is a bonus loft in the entry way - every kid's dream! The home features radiant floor heating (including the garage), and solar panels (3 years old). Across the sprawling 80 acres there is an abundance of fruit trees, grape vines, flower beds, and many fenced pen areas ready for animals. Plenty of storage in the attached two car garage, and multiple sheds. An ideal location - near hundreds of acres of public land and ORV trails, but close enough for high-speed internet. Don't miss this rare opportunity to hunt and fish on your OWN property! Call/text for a private tour today!
